    "Further Reading": "Mechanical Retrieval and Recanalization of Stroke Clots Using Embolectomy (MR RESCUE) trial details and protocol; National Institute of Neurological Disorders and Stroke (NINDS) publications."
}

{
    "Clinical Question": "In patients with minor ischemic stroke or high-risk TIA, does the addition of clopidogrel to aspirin improve outcomes?",
