    "Further Reading": "POINT ClinicalTrials.gov number, NCT00991029."
}

{
    "Clinical Question": "Among patients with recent symptomatic lacunar infarcts identified by magnetic resonance imaging, does the addition of clopidogrel to aspirin improve secondary stroke prevention?",
    "Bottom Line": "Among patients with recent lacunar strokes, the addition of clopidogrel to aspirin did not significantly reduce the risk of recurrent stroke and significantly increased the risk of bleeding and death.",
